notes: 'This configuration includes ALL features AND their output columns from feature_dependencies.yaml.


  Usage:

  1. Use this as input to ts-factor-eval to evaluate all factors

  2. Review the evaluation results and use the generated features_suggested.yaml

  3. Iteratively refine your factor selection based on IC/Sharpe metrics


  Total features: 181

  Total requested items (features + output columns): 648


  Note: This includes both feature names (for dependency resolution) and output columns
